WEBVTT



00:00:10.720 --> 00:00:11.584
Hello.

00:00:11.424 --> 00:00:15.200
My name's Derek Walker. I'm the pastor of the Oxford Bible Church.

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:19.328
Today I want to introduce you to my book called Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:00:19.456 --> 00:00:24.800
You know, God loves us all. He wants everyone to be saved. And for that reason, he has

00:00:24.672 --> 00:00:26.720
Delayed his judgment.

00:00:26.944 --> 00:00:30.560
And he wants as many people as possible to repent.

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:40.448
and to receive his salvation that he offers them as a free gift. But let us not get the wrong idea. God will judge, he must judge all sin, and there is a

00:00:39.968 --> 00:00:41.952
There is a coming, a day of judgment.

00:00:42.112 --> 00:00:52.160
And he has made that very clear in his word, and he's also made it clear by doing certain exemplary judgments in history, and one of these judgments is the judgment.

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:54.048
Of Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:00:55.264 --> 00:01:03.584
One of the great judgments of the Bible is the destruction of Solomon Gomorrah, along with the whole surrounding area of the Dead Sea.

00:01:03.616 --> 00:01:04.928
This book

00:01:04.832 --> 00:01:08.672
Is filled with photographs from the region.

00:01:08.352 --> 00:01:18.400
And it demonstrates that the remains of these cities are still there to be seen, perfectly confirming the Bible account of this dramatic divine.

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:19.360
Divine intervention.

00:01:20.160 --> 00:01:25.120
You see, God did this judgment to give a visual demonstration.

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:27.104
That we would learn by.

00:01:26.944 --> 00:01:34.112
It's a demonstration to all mankind and the Dead Sea now is a dramatic region unique on the face of the earth.

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:39.712
And we are to learn some vital spiritual lessons from this great judgment.

00:01:40.032 --> 00:01:45.696
It includes a revelation of the final judgment that God will do by fire.

00:01:45.824 --> 00:01:53.440
And so I urge you to get hold of this book and understand what God is saying through the story.

00:01:53.408 --> 00:01:55.008
On Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:01:56.608 --> 00:02:01.664
We will take you through the story of Abraham and Lot, and how God rescued Lot.

00:02:02.304 --> 00:02:12.352
We will also locate the the five cities that were destroyed in this way, and you'll be amazed to see the ashen buildings that are embedded with sulphur balls.

00:02:11.872 --> 00:02:12.800
Which?

00:02:12.576 --> 00:02:14.816
is another word for brimstone.

00:02:15.136 --> 00:02:17.568
And faced with this proof.

00:02:17.568 --> 00:02:19.296
This will stir you up.

00:02:19.456 --> 00:02:23.264
even more to get right with God and to share the gospel.

00:02:23.488 --> 00:02:26.624
There is also available a two-hour DVD

00:02:26.528 --> 00:02:30.240
documentary of Solon Gomorrah that fits with this book.
